Class TimeAllocationMutator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.core.replanning.modules.AbstractMultithreadedModule
      • org.matsim.core.replanning.modules.TimeAllocationMutator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlanStrategyModule, GenericPlanStrategyModule<Plan>

    public class TimeAllocationMutator
extends AbstractMultithreadedModule
    Wraps the PlanMutateTimeAllocation- PlanAlgorithm into a PlanStrategyModule so it can be used for plans replanning. Supports multiple threads.

    mrieser
